\section*{What is probability?}

What is probability?
\begin{itemize}
\item Who's asking?
\item Scientist: Most useful answer is a model for the world (i.e. experiments,
physics, psychology, etc)
\item Student: Most common answer: counting cards and balls in urns.
\item Philosopher: A branch of mathematics and logic.
\end{itemize}
We'll do all three.  Mostly math though.

